quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,40,"Hini na Bantwana bakwaSirayeli! Khumbulani uBabalo lwaM eNdaluthoba phezu kwenu, nizalisekise uMnqophiso wenu kuM njengoko Mna Ndawuzalisekisayo uMnqophiso waM kuni nize noyike Mna"
  2,41,Kholwani koko Ndikuthobileyo kungqina oko kukuni. Musani ukuba ngabokuqala ekungakholweni kuko oko; kananjalo musani ukuthengisa ngeMiqondiso yaM ngexabiso elincinane. Yaye futhi yoyikani Mna
  2,42,"Musani ukugqumelela inyaniso ngobuxoki, kananjalo ningayifihli inyaniso niyazi"
  2,43,Yenzani iSalâh ninikele ngomrhumo weZakâh14 niqubude kunye nabo baqubudayo
  2,44,Nina niyalela abantu ngokulungileyo nize nina nizilibale kodwa ningabafundi besiBhalo! Kanti aniqiqi na
  2,45,"Funani uncedo (kuAllâh) ngomonde nangeSalâh, inene kunzima oko kodwa hayi kwabo bantliziyo zithobekileyo"
  2,46,"Bona bakholelwayo ekubeni ngenene baya kudibana neNkosi, uMlondozi wabo nasekubeni baya kubuyela kuYo ngenene"